use the setting like this::

    (setq jedi:goto-definition-config
          '((nil definition nil)
            (t   definition nil)
            (nil nil        nil)
            (t   nil        nil)
            (nil definition t  )
            (t   definition t  )
            (nil nil        t  )
            (t   nil        t  )))

You can rearrange the order to have most useful sets of arguments
at the top."
  :group 'jedi
  :type '(repeat (choice (const nil)
                         (const t)
                         (const definition))))


